u!]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY009|Clemont\'s Got a Secret!]]\'\'.\n\nTwo Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY016|A Jolting Switcheroo!]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY026|A Battle by Any Other Name!]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY028|The Bonds of Evolution!]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY029|Heroes - Friends and Faux Alike!]]\'\'.\n\nMultiple Oddish appeared in \'\'[[M17|Diancie and the Cocoon of Destruction]]\'\' as residents of [[Allearth Forest]].\n\nAn Oddish appeared in a flashback in \'\'[[Diancie — Princess of the Diamond Domain]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in a flashback or a fantasy in \'\'[[XY035|The Forest Champion!]]\'\'.\n\nMultiple Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY057|Thawing an Icy Panic!]]\'\', with one under the ownership of a Trainer and the others being residents of [[Ramos]]\'s ranch. The Trainer\'s Oddish reappeared in \'\'[[XY059|Under the Pledging Tree!]]\'\', where it was among the Pokémon present during the [[Coumarine City Festival]].\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY073|A Fashionable Battle!]]\'\'.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[PK27|Pikachu and the Pokémon Music Squad]]\'\'. It was among the Pokémon residing in a forest.\n\nAn Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY089|A Frolicking Find in the Flowers!]]\'\'.\n\nTwo Oddish appeared in a flashback in \'\'[[XY108|A Watershed Moment!]]\'\'.\n\nA Trainer\'s Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY111|Unlocking Some Respect!]]\'\'.\n\nMultiple Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY121|Seeing the Forest for the Trees!]]\'\', one being seen in a flashback. One of them, along with a {{p|Scatterbug}}, {{p|Budew}}, {{p|Sentret}}, and {{p|Zigzagoon}}, were brought into a cave to join Ash in the [[Winding Woods]].\n\nA Trainer\'s Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY125|A League of His Own!]]\'\'.\n\nTwo Oddish appeared in \'\'[[M19|Volcanion and the Mechanical Marvel]]\'\'.\n\nA Trainer\'s Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY138|The First Day of the Rest of Your Life!]]\'\'.\n\nThree Oddish appeared in \'\'[[XY140|Till We Compete